data.description: Beautiful home with views of the lake! This property features upgrades throughout. Outside features RV parking, UGS, New Roof and exterior paint as well as a spacious backyard with fruit trees, patio and space for a garden. Upgrades inside include new lifetime windows, new interior flooring, LVP flooring, 3 year old AC unit and Heat Pump, and a brand new Kitchen with quartz countertops and new cabinets. Interior features 3 bedrooms upstairs as well as a full bath and 3/4 bath. Downstairs features 2 bedrooms, a bonus room or office space, 3/4 bath and a large living room with projector screen. Schedule your showing today and don't miss your opportunity to view this amazing property!
